    "title": "Lead Instructional Designer at IIT Madras",
    "description": "IIT Madras, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Instructional Designer for our Meerut operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout IIT Madras:\nIIT Madras is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IIT Madras!",
